{"tid":6666,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"陸客放航拍機變血滴子 大媽逛夜市遭割傷！！","createTime":"2016-11-27T13:05:59.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-28T10:31:25.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fac90069d04b4e94f4611ba05a76ec69abac89c0","tid":6666,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T13:05:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/china/20161127/55971835\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fchina%2F20161127%2F55971835&d=UFwGXX8V4%2F2YAQ8xCHZgtMW%2Flfx08C7TTpsJ%2BRLLqlo%3D&h=c51f5350\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fchina%2F20161127%2F55971835&h=b7157058\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/china/20161127/55971835</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20161127/large/1480221179_8184.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20161127%2Flarge%2F1480221179_8184.jpg&h=535b04cf&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n近年來興起航拍機熱潮，不過也常傳出傷人意外。台灣台北市議員顏若芳指，大陸遊客在台北的寧夏夜市使用航拍機，結果操作不當，其母親當時就在現場，被航拍機的螺旋槳割傷額頭和鼻部等多處受傷。顏母憶述：「不知道被甚麼東西打到，整個蹲下來，整個左臉很痛」，也不知道已經被航拍機割傷，就像血滴子一樣可怕。 <br />\n<br />\n顏若芳表示，昨晚媽媽到寧夏夜市買東西，行經至寧夏路時突然被天下掉落的航拍機擊中，當時耳邊還聽到螺旋槳轉動的聲音，接着就發現自己多處被割傷。空拍機的主人馬上致歉，還陪其母到醫院包紮傷口，她透露主人是兩名大陸自由行遊客，因為想拍寧夏夜市空景才使用航拍機。 <br />\n<br />\n台北市議員顏若芳在facebook發文寫道，有民眾在人潮眾多的寧夏夜市玩航拍機，結果操作不當，航拍機當場成為可怕的傷人血滴子，但是目前卻沒有罰則可以管。顏若芳認為，日本跟美國都有相關的航拍機規範，反觀台灣，中央規範的是25公斤以上，至於25公斤以下的交由地方政府訂制，無人航拍機已經是隨手可得的產品，相關的規範應該要儘速擬定出來，確保用路人與使用者的安全。 <br />\n<br />\n網民熱議指：「航拍機要列為管制品，無論大小都要有序號、證件，類似機車管理模式管理，操作者須上課取得證件方可在公眾場所操作。類似汽機車的強制的第三人意外險也是必要，從銷售端管理。....航拍機是高度危險產品(操作者能力優劣相對重要)，並且對不特定人的隱私也有侵犯的疑慮！！...今天是受傷，如果是砸死呢？..」。另有網民說：「業餘者要玩大型航拍機的基本原則就是，人多、鬧區不玩；飛行高度不要超過標準。然後就是盡量不要在私人不動產上面飛行停留。」"},{"pid":"98c8ffb3ddcda6e239c2623764ec07387dec0ac8","tid":6666,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T13:07:00.000Z","msg":"唔記將大媽轉做師奶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> sorry"},{"pid":"d3092ead4e721a6fbf1bdc3726f2af48dd060938","tid":6666,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T13:17:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e19a5894319487bb9b86dab6a3436e6eb7e6ca6","tid":6666,"uid":649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T13:18:26.000Z","msg":"痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a047796adbf860e10e016624ca6c3328e0fcfcf","tid":6666,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T14:06:14.000Z","msg":"死圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65659b583b48af5541f07a5974f292aa7eec8a4a","tid":6666,"uid":11753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T16:56:26.000Z","msg":"屌你老味又係大陸屄"},{"pid":"fe62aefcb2f0b91572e08e3a91ed4edb3030467a","tid":6666,"uid":13420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T16:57:48.000Z","msg":"好撚鳩屎 係夜市放航拍機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d3d0e49be81aaae73fed2485d883ece0256b599","tid":6666,"uid":25350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T19:05:27.000Z","msg":"香港都周街有人玩冇管制<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a90d7c8d18df619550ba76823d0efe833ea0ed4","tid":6666,"uid":26156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T19:09:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ad1cc955cac269d6c93ab667837c9c489979cc0b","tid":6666,"uid":3189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T19:23:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/china/20161127/55971835\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fchina%2F20161127%